  "bio_raw": "Md. Ahsan Ullah serves as a lecturer in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering (CSE) at the University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB). He earned his B.Sc. in mathematics from Khulna University, Bangladesh. Then he obtained his M.Sc. in Applied Mathematics from the same institution.\nResearch interests: mathematics modeling, dynamical systems, machine learning, and deep learning. He is especially fascinated by the potential of mathematical foundations in problem resolution or technological advancements.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Mathematical Modelling, Applied and Computational Mathematics, Numerical Simulation, Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Data Science, Image Processing, Computer Vision, Pattern Recognition."
  ],
  "education": [
    {
      "raw": "Education\nMaster of Science\nin Applied Mathematics, Khulna University, Khulna, Bangladesh.\nBachelor of Science (Honors)\nin Mathematics, Khulna University, Khulna, Bangladesh."
    }
